      <title>伊拉克油田发生火灾导致上月 OPEC 产量下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/opec-output-dipped-last-month-following-fire-at-iraqi-oil-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社调查显示，受伊拉克最大油田发生火灾影响，上个月欧佩克石油产量小幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/opec-output-dipped-last-month-following-fire-at-iraqi-oil-field</guid>
