    <item>
      <title>BMO 的戴维斯表示，贸易战可能引发通胀冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trade-war-could-cause-inflation-shock-says-bmo-s-davis-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BMO 全球资产管理公司固定收益和货币市场主管 Earl Davis 表示，与墨西哥和加拿大的贸易和关税战可能导致通胀冲击。他谈到了对全球债券市场的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trade-war-could-cause-inflation-shock-says-bmo-s-davis-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰森食品利润猛增 为特朗普贸易战做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-as-chicken-drives-strong-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司表示，由于关税威胁到其对墨西哥的猪肉出口，该公司正在努力应对唐纳德·特朗普发起的贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-as-chicken-drives-strong-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税推迟，墨西哥比索兑美元大幅反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国对墨西哥征收关税将推迟一个月的消息影响，墨西哥比索引领大盘反弹，而美元则几乎抹去了涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥关税推迟一个月，欧洲股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希恩鲍姆 (Claudia Sheinbaum) 表示，在与唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 通话后，美国将推迟一个月实施征收的关税，欧洲股市削减了早前的跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/european-stock-futures-slide-as-trump-eyes-next-round-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
